        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Insights &<br>
          <span class="text-accent-primary">Blog Post</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Real stories from the job site, honest advice from our team, and the latest news 
